{"id":77233,"title":"[Frontotemporal Dementia (FTD) - even with revisited criteria a diagnostic challenge].","abstract":"Frontotemporal dementia remains a diagnostic challenge. Especially the differential diagnosis between FTD and affective disorders is often difficult. Based on a case report, diagnostic efforts and differential diagnoses are described and revisited criteria for the behavioral FTD (bvFTD) from Rascowsky et al. are mentioned. ","date":"2014-05-14","categories":"Nutritional and Metabolic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24824204","annotations":[{"name":"Dementia","weight":0.797552,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dementia"},{"name":"Differential diagnosis","weight":0.793943,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_diagnosis"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.74384,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Behavior","weight":0.693915,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Behavior"},{"name":"Affect (psychology)","weight":0.678276,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Affect_(psychology)"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.566594,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Affective spectrum","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Affective_spectrum"},{"name":"Frontotemporal dementia","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frontotemporal_dementia"},{"name":"Differential (mechanical device)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_(mechanical_device)"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.01376,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"}]}
